```WEBVTT

00:00.960 --> 00:01.600
<v Agent>Good afternoon.

00:01.600 --> 00:02.240
<v Agent>This is Sam.

00:02.240 --> 00:03.280
<v Agent>Thank you for calling Contoso.

00:03.280 --> 00:03.920
<v Agent>How can I help?

00:05.040 --> 00:05.440
<v Customer>Hi there.

00:05.440 --> 00:06.240
<v Customer>My name is Mary.

00:06.240 --> 00:09.280
<v Customer>I'm currently living in Los Angeles, but I'm planning to move to Las Vegas.

00:09.280 --> 00:10.560
<v Customer>I would like to apply for a loan.

00:12.640 --> 00:12.840
<v Agent>Okay.

00:13.120 --> 00:14.800
<v Agent>I see you're currently living in California.

00:14.800 --> 00:16.640
<v Agent>Let me make sure I understand you correctly.

00:17.120 --> 00:19.720
<v Agent>Uh You'd like to apply for a loan even though you'll be moving soon.

00:19.720 --> 00:20.200
<v Agent>Is that right?

00:21.440 --> 00:22.400
<v Customer>Yes, exactly.

00:22.560 --> 00:27.280
<v Customer>So I'm planning to relocate soon, but I would like to apply for the loan first so that I can purchase a new home once I move there.

00:28.880 --> 00:30.800
<v Agent>And are you planning to sell your current home?

00:32.000 --> 00:35.440
<v Customer>Yes, I will be listing it on the market soon and hopefully it'll sell quickly.

00:35.800 --> 00:41.120
<v Customer>That's why I'm applying for a loan now, so that I can purchase a new house in Nevada and close on it quickly as well once my current home sells.

00:42.560 --> 00:42.880
<v Agent>I see.

00:43.680 --> 00:46.240
<v Agent>Would you mind holding for a moment while I take your information down?

00:47.200 --> 00:47.920
<v Customer>Yeah, no problem.

00:47.920 --> 00:48.640
<v Customer>Thank you for your help.

00:50.120 --> 00:50.720
<v Agent>Mm-hmm.

00:50.720 --> 00:51.440
<v Agent>Just one moment.

00:58.800 --> 00:59.040
<v Agent>All right.

00:59.040 --> 01:00.520
<v Agent>Thank you for your patience, ma'am.

01:00.520 --> 01:02.640
<v Agent>May I have your first and last name, please?

01:03.520 --> 01:05.520
<v Customer>Yes, my name is Mary Smith.

01:07.600 --> 01:08.280
<v Agent>Thank you, Ms.

01:08.280 --> 01:08.640
<v Agent>Smith.

01:08.960 --> 01:10.400
<v Agent>May I have your current address, please?

01:11.520 --> 01:11.800
<v Customer>Yes.

01:11.800 --> 01:18.640
<v Customer>So my address is 123 Main Street in Los Angeles, California, and the zip code is 90923.

01:20.480 --> 01:22.720
<v Agent>Sorry, that was a 90 what?

01:24.160 --> 01:26.160
<v Customer>90923.

01:27.680 --> 01:30.880
<v Agent>90923 on Main Street.

01:30.880 --> 01:31.200
<v Agent>Got it.

01:31.520 --> 01:32.000
<v Agent>Thank you.

01:32.240 --> 01:33.680
<v Agent>May I have your phone number as well, please?

01:33.680 --> 01:33.720
<v Agent>Uh.

01:34.960 --> 01:42.480
<v Customer>Yes, my phone number is 504-529-2351 and then yeah.

01:43.600 --> 01:44.880
<v Agent>2351.

01:46.640 --> 01:46.880
<v Agent>Got it.

01:47.520 --> 01:52.480
<v Agent>And do you have an e-mail address we I can associate with this application?

01:53.640 --> 01:56.640
<v Customer>Uh Yes, so my e-mail address is mary.a.sm78@gmail.com.

02:02.640 --> 02:08.240
<v Agent>Mary.a, was that a S-N as in November or M as in Mike?

02:09.520 --> 02:10.320
<v Customer>M as in Mike.

02:11.520 --> 02:14.560
<v Agent>Mike78, got it.

02:14.560 --> 02:15.120
<v Agent>Thank you.

02:15.160 --> 02:15.320
<v Agent>Ms.

02:15.320 --> 02:17.920
<v Agent>Smith, do you currently have any other loans?

02:19.520 --> 02:22.240
<v Customer>Uh Yes, so I currently have two other loans through Contoso.

02:22.720 --> 02:25.840
<v Customer>So my first one is my car loan and then my other is my student loan.

02:26.080 --> 02:30.680
<v Customer>They total about 1400 per month combined and my interest rate is 8%.

02:30.680 --> 02:30.840
<v Customer>I see.

02:30.840 --> 02:31.040
<v Customer>And.

02:32.960 --> 02:35.360
<v Agent>You're currently paying those loans off monthly, is that right?

02:36.400 --> 02:37.200
<v Customer>Yes, of course I do.

02:39.280 --> 02:40.000
<v Agent>OK, thank you.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.520
<v Agent>Here's what I suggest we do.

02:41.520 --> 02:47.600
<v Agent>Let me place you on a brief hold again so that I can talk with one of our loan officers and get this started for you immediately.

02:48.000 --> 02:57.360
<v Agent>In the meantime, it would be great if you could take a few minutes and complete the remainder of the secure application online at www.contosoloans.com.

02:58.400 --> 02:59.240
<v Customer>Yeah, that sounds good.

02:59.240 --> 03:00.240
<v Customer>I can go ahead and get started.

03:00.320 --> 03:01.000
<v Customer>Thank you for your help.

03:01.960 --> 03:02.240
<v Agent>Thank you.```

Summary.valueString: Mary Smith called Contoso to inquire about applying for a loan to purchase a new home in Las Vegas. She is currently living in Los Angeles and plans to sell her current home. Mary has two existing loans with Contoso, a car loan and a student loan, totaling $1400 per month with an 8% interest rate. The agent, Sam, collected her personal information and suggested she complete the secure application online while he consults with a loan officer.
